beginning, containing an area of TWO THOUSAND SIX HUNDRED SEVENTY SIX (2,676) SQUARE METERS , more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PLS Cylindrical Concrete Mohons 15 x 60 centimeters; bearings true; date of the original survey, December 1910 to June 1911 (Marikina Estate) and that of the subdivision survey, October 18, 2004 and approved on November 18, 2004.

Riverbanks Center ICT Building II Lot No. 2 Pcs-00-011289

A parcel of land (Lot 2 of the consolidation-subdivision plan Pcs-00-011289, being a consolidation of Lots 1-A and 1-B, Psd-00-055453, L.R.C. Record No. 7672) situated in the Barangay of Barangka, City of Marikina, Metro Manila, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the NW. and SE., along lines 1-2-3 by Lot 1 of the consolidation-subdivision plan; and on the SW., along line 3-4-5-6-1 by the Lot 49-C-3-A-3-C-A-6-B-1 (LRC) Psd-79.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being S. 65 deg. 21′ W., 1,648.68 m. from B.L.L.M. No. 2, Marikina, Rizal (now City of Marikina);

