beginning, containing an area of FOURTEEN THOUSAND SIX HUNDRED SIXTY SEVEN (14,667) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PS cylindrical concrete mohons 15 x 60 centimeters; bearings true; date of the original survey, December 1910 to June 1911 (Marikina Estate) and that of the consolidation-subdivision; date of survey, October 18, 2004 and approved on November 18, 2004.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done, in the City of Manila this 28th day of January in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

